\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Per-circuit Δviolation and ΔHPWL means (\,$\pm $\,std), 4 seeds each. Negative is improvement. VSR-post is the only method with consistent positive (\,fewer violations\,) results across all 6 circuits without catastrophically inflating HPWL.}}{5}{table.caption.19}\protected@file@percent }
