\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Intra-sampling HPWL change as a function of $t_{\text  {start}}$, across 6 circuits and 3 seeds. Bigblue3 (the largest tractable circuit) shows a striking monotonic improvement, peaking at $-34.5\%$ HPWL. Smaller circuits show small effects, suggesting backbone-prior leverage scales with circuit size.}}{6}{figure.caption.22}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:timestep_sweep}{{1}{6}{Intra-sampling HPWL change as a function of $t_{\text {start}}$, across 6 circuits and 3 seeds. Bigblue3 (the largest tractable circuit) shows a striking monotonic improvement, peaking at $-34.5\%$ HPWL. Smaller circuits show small effects, suggesting backbone-prior leverage scales with circuit size}{figure.caption.22}{}}
