\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4}{\ignorespaces bigblue3 (1298 macros, seed=42). The raw diffusion draft (left) piles macros at a corner. Post-processing VSR-post (middle) spreads them out to achieve $-79\%$ violations but grows wirelength by $18\%$. Intra-sampling VSR-intra (right) retains a compact layout that respects the diffusion backbone's implicit wirelength prior, achieving the strongest HPWL reduction.}}{10}{figure.caption.34}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:postvsintra}{{4}{10}{bigblue3 (1298 macros, seed=42). The raw diffusion draft (left) piles macros at a corner. Post-processing VSR-post (middle) spreads them out to achieve $-79\%$ violations but grows wirelength by $18\%$. Intra-sampling VSR-intra (right) retains a compact layout that respects the diffusion backbone's implicit wirelength prior, achieving the strongest HPWL reduction}{figure.caption.34}{}}
